37
00:01:22,230 --> 00:01:25,430
money put, and simultaneously selling to open an

38
00:01:25,430 --> 00:01:26,370
out of the money call.

39
00:01:26,910 --> 00:01:29,070
We would do this in hopes that between

40
00:01:29,070 --> 00:01:31,830
now and expiration, the stock will stay in

41
00:01:31,830 --> 00:01:34,050
between the strikes and the options we sold

42
00:01:34,050 --> 00:01:35,130
will go to zero.

43
00:01:35,590 --> 00:01:37,210
If this is the case, we will keep

44
00:01:37,210 --> 00:01:39,350
the entire price we sold these options for.

45
00:01:40,030 --> 00:01:42,190
But since short naked options can have a

46
00:01:42,190 --> 00:01:43,930
lot of risk and can require a lot

47
00:01:43,930 --> 00:01:46,290
of capital, we are also going to buy

48
00:01:46,290 --> 00:01:48,390
a further out of the money put and

49
00:01:48,390 --> 00:01:49,310
