76
00:02:41,870 --> 00:02:44,470
Let's say we initiated this trade with 30

77
00:02:44,470 --> 00:02:45,530
days to expiration.

78
00:02:46,250 --> 00:02:48,570
And as time passes and we near expiration,

79
00:02:49,050 --> 00:02:50,910
let's say the stock doesn't move much and

80
00:02:50,910 --> 00:02:53,050
just kind of bounces around and trades sideways.

81
00:02:53,510 --> 00:02:56,530
So as we near expiration, these options remain

82
00:02:56,530 --> 00:02:58,190
