93
00:03:18,170 --> 00:03:20,070
Okay, but we also lost some money on

94
00:03:20,070 --> 00:03:21,490
the options we bought as protection.

95
00:03:21,970 --> 00:03:24,910
We lost $100 on the 90 strike call

96
00:03:24,910 --> 00:03:27,630
and also on the 60 strike put, because

97
00:03:27,630 --> 00:03:29,510
